00:05:15,301 --> 00:05:17,418
will be negative.

54
00:05:17,555 --> 00:05:22,189
Therefore we will not have 
right-handed waves

55
00:05:22,826 --> 00:05:27,899
and similarly for the left-handed waves 
this term and this term here

