00:05:36,712 --> 00:05:41,657
and in particular we see that for...

59
00:05:42,199 --> 00:05:49,843
- as typically the ion cyclotron
frequency is much smaller than ωL,

60
00:05:49,956 --> 00:05:58,004
... that for frequencies between 
the ion cyclotron frequency Ωi and ωL,

61
00:05:58,659 --> 00:06:01,082
we have no left-handed waves.

62
00:06:01,232 --> 00:06:06,496
If we draw a diagram that represents 
the frequency

63
00:06:06,496 --> 00:06:12,380
as a function of the wavenumber,
the frequencies of interest will be

64
00:06:14,048 --> 00:06:18,683
along this scale located 
