65
00:06:18,683 --> 00:06:20,397
Ωi,

66
00:06:20,861 --> 00:06:29,142
then ωL, then the electron 
cyclotron frequency |Ωe|, and ωR

67
00:06:30,061 --> 00:06:36,415
and in this region
we won't have left-handed waves

68
00:06:37,781 --> 00:06:42,107
and similarly in this region we won't have
