69
00:06:44,475 --> 00:06:50,768
A second thing that may be interesting 
to look at is how these waves behave

70
00:06:50,768 --> 00:06:53,253
when ω tends to infinity.

71
00:06:53,776 --> 00:06:56,408
In this case, we will have that 
K² c² / ω²

72
00:06:59,095 --> 00:07:06,546
will tend to -- ω will tend to infinity 
both this fraction and this fraction here

