00:13:17,508 --> 00:13:19,348
they are called <i>whistler waves</i>.

140
00:13:19,658 --> 00:13:21,395
Let's look at this property.

141
00:13:21,843 --> 00:13:24,834
So we will consider 
the right-handed waves

