00:13:40,739 --> 00:13:44,487
that is typically smaller 
or comparable

147
00:13:44,487 --> 00:13:50,984
to the electron cyclotron frequency |Ωe|
and the frequency ωR .

148
00:13:52,088 --> 00:13:56,546
Where are we in 
