00:16:52,871 --> 00:16:57,530
and therefore this 1 can be 
neglected with respect to this term.

181
00:16:57,709 --> 00:17:01,771
This is therefore equal to 
ωpe² / ( ω |Ωe|)

182
00:17:04,705 --> 00:17:07,286
Here we've got a relatively simple result

